description:
Description
A regular time series giving the monthly totals of car drivers in
Great Britain killed or seriously injured Jan 1969 to Dec
1984.  Compulsory wearing of seat belts was introduced on 31 Jan 1983
title: Deaths of Car Drivers in Great Britain 1969-84
format:
Harvey, A.C. (1989)
Forecasting, Structural Time Series Models and the Kalman Filter.
Cambridge University Press, pp. 519–523.
